\id 2PE Reconstructed from Ventura Publisher
\h 2 Pita
\toc1 Khe Pita Phenat…®t…®gap Khergi Gap
\toc2 2 Pita
\toc3 2 Pi
\mt1 2 PITA
\mt2 Khe Pita Phenat…®t…®gap Khergi Gap
\imt1 Khe fharav gan…®nga buni khare.
\ip Pita kha gava khergi kama n…®…®eŇč khaŇč muuŇčgi. Fhura wari ga sh…®sh…®gap Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuav ntan gumgi gu mbigi kh…®va rui gumgi mbari, mbe ruim, Pita kha gava khergiap, mba guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi ndi mbav, khaŇč mbe nzuai. Nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, nde mba fhura wari ga sh…®sh…®ga Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuav nta gumgi gu mbigi kh…®vi gumgi, nde mbe nzuai buni mbarara thari. Mbe nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi nd…®knd…®gi, mbe ntan farfav, vh…®ra nden t…®vir vhuuin farfagi. Nde mba Zisas farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi nde kh…®vav nde suaŇčgi buni, nde guigira nta suirav havhargiri. Nde maaŇč muuŇčv, nde tuituigip Fhe Bak…®me kaŇčgip, vh…®ra Guma Bak…®me Zisas Krais kaŇčgirga. Mba Zisas farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi, mbe wari won r…®mgi thugira Zisas gangi. Mbe vh…®ra wari wo khuarira Zisas mbararagim, ana mbe kh…®vav mbe suaŇčgi.
\ip Mbe gumgi mbari khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúZisas taagi zirg…®rga fhu.‚ÄĚ Kha gap maaŇč nzuai fhu. Kha gap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúAna taagi zir…®rga.‚ÄĚ KhueŇč guigira, ana vhemkora zirg…®rga fhuvara. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®me kha nuianan ki guma the fh…®rgi r…®g…®p, Herar Ňčg…®rgeŇč vuzvugi fhu. Ana khueŇč vuzvugi, kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi, mbe za ndavi domdorgip guigira Zisas khoth…®g…®ri. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgiap, mbarara kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi rargap khar ki. (3.9)
\c 1
\ms1 Nza khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip, t…®vir vhuuin muuŇčrim, nta khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip, nzan k…®rga, nza mba gumgi mbat…®gi nzuai buni, nza nta daaŇčgip mbur kh…®ngirga.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt 2 Ko 4.13; Ef 4.5; Ta 1.4\x*Gu Saimon Pita, gu Zisas Krais farasarigi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara guma mbe ma. Gu vh…®ra ana Ňčaara guma ma. Ana nza Fhe Bak…®me ma. Ana taagi nza ndi guma ma. Gu kha gava khergiap, nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gap, nd…®knd…®ga vhuuŇč ndigi gumgi gu mbigi, gu anan nde ndi mbai. Nde Zisas Kraisan t…®var vhuuŇč, nde guigira ana khoth…®gi t…®v, ana guigira nza ana khoth…®gi t…®vara fara muuŇčgi.
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Zu 1.2\x*Nde ntigem tuituigiap Fhe Bak…®me kaŇčgiap, nza wo Bak…®me Zisas, nde vh…®ra ana kaŇčgi. Nde mba t…®va mbuim, Fhe Bak…®men kora muumbar gum ana ndava m…®…®t…®k k…®vgip, nden ndavi vherir k…®v k…®rar h…®ri.
\s1 Fhe Bak…®me nzan wora mbuigi.
\p 
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Zo 17.3; 2 Te 2.14; 2 T 1.9; 1 Pi 2.9\x*Zisas Krais, ana Fhe Bak…®me ma. Ana won ŇčkasŇčkar, ana za kha bigir nza n…®…®Ňčgi. Mba bigi nza kha ki k…®r…® t…®vi havharap nzan kurkurigim, nza Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčgi t…®vi z…®n vui. Nza mba t…®vir muun zav, ana fhura nza garim, nza tuituigiap ana kaŇčgi. Ana wo z…® bak…®me gum, won ŇčkasŇčka bak…®me gum, won t…®var vhuuŇč guarara, nza ana phorg…®v mba bigi ndir zav, ana nzan kamgi.
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt 2 Ko 7.1; Ef 4.24; 2 Pi 2.18-20; 1 Zo 3.2\x*Ana nzan kamgiap, ana bigi vhuuiŇč guarira gum guigira bigi bak…®vira nza n…®…®Ňčgi. Mba bigi, ana fhum ntan nzan n…®…®n za suaŇčgi. Nza kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi, nza bigi garav, nta nzuav ndavi khavi t…®vi, nta nzan ndavi vherir kav, nza muuŇčgim, nza guigira mbat…®gi. Ana guigira bigir vhuuiŇč guarira nza n…®…®Ňčgi. Ana nden kurkura zav mba t…®va muuŇčgi. Ana maaŇč nden muuŇčgirim, nde mba t…®vi mbat…®gi Ňčk…®…®av, nde ana k…®r…® t…®vi gum ana t…®vi ndirga.
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt 1 Pi 3.7; 2 Pi 3.18\x*Ana maaŇč muuŇčgim, nde mba bigi ga nd…®knd…®g…®p, nde khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip, guigira Zisas khoth…®g…®ri. Nde ana khoth…®gi t…®vara, nde t…®vir vhuuin muuŇčri. Nde t…®vir vhuuiaŇč mbui t…®vara, nde Fhe Bak…®me kaŇčgiri. Nde ana kaŇčgi t…®vara, nde tuituigip wari wo vuzvugi gan…®ri.
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt Ga 5.22-23\x*Nde tuituigip wari wo vuzvugi gari t…®vara, nde thivgip, havhargip, simt…®gi ndiri. Nde thivgiap, havhargiap, simt…®gi ndi t…®vara, nde Fhe Bak…®men t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…®ri. Nde Fhe Bak…®men t…®vi z…®n vui t…®vara, nde fegi gu Ňčgugi g…®rg…®ri k…®ri.
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Ga 6.10; 1 Te 5.15; 1 Zo 4.21\x*Nde fegi gu Ňčgugi g…®rg…®ri ki t…®vara, nde guigira wari won ndavir harigi nt…®…®rir n…®…®Ňčri.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Zo 15.2; Ta 3.14\x*Nde nza wo Bak…®me Zisas Krais, nde ana kaŇčgi. Nde mba t…®vi ndigirim, nta khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip nden k…®rga, mba t…®vi, nta fhura nden keg…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Mba t…®vi, nta khaŇč t…®g…®p k…®vgip, nden k…®v, nta guigira mba vh…®rve teg…®rga.
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Hi 9.14; 1 Zo 1.7; 2.9-11\x*Mba t…®vi ki fhuv gumgi, mbe saman ki bigi, mbe nta gangirga tukt…®gi fhuvara, mbe r…®mgi mbat…®gi gumgi farar muuŇčgip k…®rga. KhueŇč guigi guarara, Fhe Bak…®me mbe fhum muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi, ana nta vh…®zgim, mbe Ňčgarigi. Mba khesharigi gumgi, mbe Fhe Bak…®me mbe muuŇčgi bigi, mbe nta nd…®knd…®gi Ňčangi.
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt 2 Pi 3.17; 1 Zo 3.19\x*Nde guigira nza phorgap Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, Fhe Bak…®me nden kamgiap, nden wora mbuigi, nde ana gumgi gu mbigi ma. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip, anan gumgi gu mbigi guarira k…®ri. Nde maaŇč muunga, nde r…®g…®p, ana tharga fhu.
\v 11 Nde maaŇč muunga, ana nde suaŇčv za tuav fhog…®rga, nde ana wo gumgi gu mbigi gari Ňčgun Ňčgirg…®p, zazera mbara muuŇčgip k…®rga. Mba Ňčgu Zisas Krais zazera ana gan…®nga ana Zisas Kraisan Ňčgu ma. Ana nza Bak…®me ma! Ana vh…®ra taagia nza ndi guma ma!
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt Fi 3.1; 1 Pi 5.12; 2 Pi 3.1; 3.17; 1 Zo 2.21; Zu 1.5\x*KhueŇč guigira, nde mba bigi kaŇčgiap, nde mba buna vhuueŇč, nde ne ndigap, nde ne th…®ga havhargi. Gu khueŇč vuzvugi, nde mba bigi, nde nta nd…®knd…®k Ňčan…® thari. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgip, zazera nde suangeŇč vuzvugi.
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt Zo 21.18-19; 2 Ko 5.1; 2 T 4.6; 2 Pi 3.1\x*Gu ntigem Ňčam kav, gu kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, ntigem tugar vhuuŇč ma. Gu wom kha bunin nde suaŇčv, nde nd…®knd…®gi khav…®rga, nde taagi mba bigi ga nd…®knd…®g…®rga.
\v 14 Gu kaŇčgi, gu r…®m…®nga tuk han mbarigi. Nza Bak…®me Zisas Krais maaŇč na suaŇčgi.
\v 15 MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, gu khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargiap, tuituigip nde suangeŇč vuzvugi. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgip rimgirga, nde zazera gu mba nde suaŇčgi bigi, nde taagi nta nd…®knd…®g…®rga.
\s1 Zisas farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi, mbe Fhe Bak…®men vhava Ňčaara garim, ana Zisasan ki.
\p 
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt 1 Ko 1.17; 1 Zo 1.1\x*Nza wari wo Bak…®me Zisas Krais wo ŇčkasŇčka bak…®me phorg…®p taagi zir…®rgane bun nde suaŇčgi. Nza mba Krais taagi zir…®rgane bun nde nzuav, nza fhura sh…®sh…®gap guma wo nd…®knd…®gar nzuai suambarar nde muuŇčgi fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Nza wari won r…®mgira Fhe Bak…®men vhava Ňčaar gum ana ŇčkasŇčka garim, ni anan kegap him, nza ni gangiap, nza ne bun nde nzuai. \f a \fr 1:16 \ft Kha kameŇč, ne Zisas fhav harigi khesharigi. Ndu Matiu 17.1 keg…®p gan…® Ňčg…®p ves 13 th…®g…®ri. Ndu vh…®ra Mak 9.2 keg…®p gan…® Ňčg…®p ves 13 th…®g…®ri. Ndu vh…®ra Ruk 9.28 keg…®p gan…® Ňčg…®p ves 36 th…®g…®ri. \f*
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Mt 3.17\x*\x - \xo 1:17 \xt Mt 17.1-5; Mk 9.2-7; Ru 9.28-35\x*Nza Ndia Fhe Bak…®me z…® bak…®men ana n…®…®Ňčgiap, mba vhava Ňčaara vhuun ana n…®…®Ňčgim, ana anan kav hi. Fhe Bak…®me, ana nduara Hevenan mba vhava Ňčaara vhuun kav, khaŇč Zisas ga nzuai, ‚ÄúKhe nan Kam ma. Gu guigira won ndavar ana n…®…®Ňčgiap, ana ndikndigi!‚ÄĚ
\v 18 Nza ana phorgap mba mb…®ksh…®man Ňčaarar kav, nza Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč mbararagim, ana Hevenan kav, maaŇč suaŇčgi.
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt Sng 119.105; Zo 5.35; VB 2.28\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nza guigira khaŇč t…®ga havhargiap, mba Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč gumgi suaŇčgi buni, nza guigira nta khoth…®gi. Nde vh…®ra, mbe suaŇčgi buni, nde nta suira havhargirga, ne nzerarga. Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč gumgi nzuai buni, nta rama fara muuŇčgiap g…®ng…®ngi ŇčaneŇč ga ntorgap kav shi. Mba ram, ana mbara muuŇčgip shiv k…®rim, Zisas taagi zir…®rga raan m…®n thug…®rga. Nden ndavi vheri Krais ntan vhen k…®v, ana nta sh…®rarga, nta mba m…®n gorim, manera ndai kam kha nuiana sh…®rigi farar muuŇčgip nta shararga. \f b \fr 1:19 \ft Mba m…®n gorim manera ndai kam, ana Zisas ma. Ndu Vhagi Buni ndi hiaŇč r…®gi gap sapta 22 ves 16 gan…®ri. \f*
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt FG 1.16; 3.18; Ro 12.6; 2 T 3.16; 1 Pi 1.11\x*Nde kaŇčgirga, big…®na bak…®m guareŇčra khare, ne khaŇč muuŇčgi.
\p Nza fhura wari won nd…®knd…®gira, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gavar, ana buna thueŇč, nza Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč gumgi nzuai mbugum, mba buna n…®…®eŇč bun suaŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara.
\v 21 Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, guma the wo nd…®knd…®gara Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč guma buni bun nzuai mbugum, buna thueŇč suaŇčgi fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar, ana nduara mba gumgi ndavi khavav, ana nduara Fhe Bak…®me bunin mbe nd…®…®im, mbe ana buni bun nzuai.
\c 2
\s1 Gumgi mbat…®gi, mbe guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigir nd…®knd…®gir farfav, mben nd…®knd…®gi Ňčgi.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt Mt 24.11; FG 20.30; 1 Ko 6.20; Ef 1.7; 1 T 4.1; 2 T 3.1-5; 1 Pi 1.18; Zu 1.4\x*KhueŇč guigi guarara, Fhe Bak…®men kamthooŇč gumgir wari guiguigi gumgi mbari, mbe IsreriŇč r…®gar hegi. Mba t…®vara fhura Fhe Bak…®men kamthooŇč gumgir wari ga sh…®sh…®gi gumgi thari, nde r…®gar heg…®p, fhura Fhe Bak…®men bigir nde gumgi gu mbigi guiguigip, mbe kh…®v…®v nde suanga. Mbe zomzor…®v, nde r…®gar mbark…®rga t…®vir nde guiguigip, nde suanga. Mba buni nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gi nd…®knd…®gir farfagirga. Nza Gari Guma Bak…®me mbe nzuav rimgiap, mbe vhezgi, mbe k…®r ana seg…®rga. Mbe mba t…®var muuŇčv, mbe nduarira vhemkora mbat…®girga.
\v 2 Gumgi vh…®rve mbe mbui t…®vi mbat…®gi z…®n Ňčg…®rga. Mbe mbui t…®vi gumgi vh…®rver muuŇčrim, mbe buni mbat…®gir t…®vi guari hi tuav ga suanga.
\v 3 \x - \xo 2:3 \xt Ro 16.18; 2 Ko 12.17-18; 1 Te 2.5; 1 T 6.5; Ta 1.11; 2 Pi 1.16\x*Mba gumgi, mbe guigira bigi niihi gumgi ma. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, mbe bigi vh…®rver nde guiguigip, nde suaŇčv nden Ňčk…®…®a gu bigi Ňčg…®rga. Mbe maaŇč nden muunga, Fhe Bak…®me fhum guarara mba khesharigi gumgi ga suaŇčv suanga tuga sarigi. Ana khaŇč mbe suaŇčgi, mbe fh…®rireg…®p, Ňčgu mbat…®gar Ňčgeg…®rga. Mba mben h…®rga big…®na mbat…®geŇč, ne kui fhuvara. Ne mben rarga mbur ki.
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Ru 8.31; Zo 8.44; 1 Zo 3.8; Zu 1.6; VB 20.2-3\x*Nde kaŇčgi, fhum Fhe Bak…®me enseri mbari, maaŇč muuŇčgiap t…®va mbat…®ga mueŇč muuŇčgim, Fhe Bak…®me fhura mbe gangi fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Ana mbe ndim, Herar mba guigira g…®ng…®ngi mbok kh…®ngim, mbe anan ki. Mbe mba b…®nan kav, mbe Fhe Bak…®me za kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi ga suaŇčv mbe suanga tugar rargap mbur ki.
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt Stt 6.1‚Äď7.24; 8.18; Hi 11.7; 1 Pi 3.20; 2 Pi 3.6\x*Mba fhum kegi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe vh…®ra k…®r Fhe Bak…®me segim, ana fhura mbe gangi fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Ana mb…® bak…®me sarigim, ana zerav, vhuuŇčgia ndav, mbe kharigim, mbe vh…®zgiap, fh…®reregi. Mba tugen, Noa, ana nduara, Fhe Bak…®men t…®vir vhuuiŇč bun nzuai guma ma. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, Fhe Bak…®me ana garav, vh…®ra harath…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, ana mbe garim, mbe nzerara kegi, mbe vh…®zgi fhuvara.
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt Stt 19.24; Nam 26.10; Zu 1.7\x*Fhe Bak…®me vh…®ra khaŇč Sodom gu Gomora suaŇčgi, mani vh…®ra mbat…®girga. Fhe Bak…®me maaŇč mani ga suaŇčgiap, ana vhavar mba Ňčgu bak…®ni kh…®ngim, mani vh…®ra shigim, manin shin…®ni ntige mbur ki. Ana mba t…®var mba Ňčgu bak…®ni ga muuŇčgim, mani za mbat…®gi. MaaŇč muuŇčgip, zumgum, gumgi gu mbigi, mbe k…®r Fhe Bak…®me s…®v, mbe mba Sodom gu Gomorar h…®gi bigeŇč, mbe ne ga nd…®knd…®g…®rga. Mbe ne ga nd…®knd…®g…®p, mbe vh…®ra warir h…®rga bigeŇč, mbe ne kaŇčgirga.
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt Stt 19.1-16\x*Mba tugen, t…®vir vhuuiaŇč mbui guma Rot, ana Sodoman ki. Ana kav, mba t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui gumgi mbui t…®vi garim, mbe mbark…®rga t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbuav, fhura ferferav ruarir wari ndi t…®vi mbat…®gi, mbe Sodoman nta mbui. Rot mbe t…®vi gangiap, ana guigira ndav simgi. Mba tugen, Fhe Bak…®me taagiap Rot ndigim, ana mbat…®gi fhu.
\v 8 AhaŇč, mba t…®vir vhuuiaŇč mbui guma, ana SodomiŇč r…®gar kav, mbe mbui t…®vi mbat…®gi garav, ana rari tug…®rat…®gap, mbe nzuai buni mbat…®gi mbararagi. Ana mben han kav, ana nd…®knd…®k gum anan ndava vhee nzerara ki. Ana kav, mbe mbui t…®vi daaŇčsur zav, ana ndav Ňčgarav guigira zaa mbat…®k hi.
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt Sng 34.17-19; 1 Ko 10.13; Zu 1.6\x*Nza Fhe Bak…®me muuŇčgi bigi, nza nta nd…®knd…®gap, nza kaŇčgi. MaaŇč muuŇčgip, mparmpare the Fhe Bak…®me z…®n vui guma then h…®g…®rga, Guma Bak…®me taagi mbe ndirga tuav, ana ana kaŇčgi. Ana taagi mbe ndig…®rga. Guma Bak…®me, ana mba gumgi mbat…®gi mbui t…®vi, ana nta kaŇčgi. Ana ne suaŇčv vheza mbat…®gar mben n…®…®nga tuap, ana vh…®ra ana kaŇčgi. Ana ne suaŇčv vheza mbat…®gar mben n…®…®Ňčv, ana vh…®ra mba Fhe Bak…®me mben t…®vi mbat…®gi ga suaŇčv mbe suanga tuga bak…®men rarga ki.
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt Zu 1.4-10; 1.16\x*Gumgi thari, mbe guigira k…®vgip, vheza mbat…®ga ndigirga.
\p Mba gumgi, mbe ruarir mbigi gu gumgi wari ndi t…®vi mbat…®gi guarira mbuav, kha nd…®knd…®gi ga mbui, Guma Bak…®me buni, nta fhura ki buni ma. Nza nta piin k…®v, nta z…®n Ňčg…®g…®rga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Mba khesharigi gumgi mbat…®gi nden r…®gar hegi. Mbe r…®…®r…®…®v, wari wo vuzvugi z…®n vui nt…®…®ri ma. Mbe maaŇč mbuav, mbe kha buivar ki ŇčiniŇčgi, mbe buni mbat…®gir mbe suangen r…®vi fhu.
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Zu 1.9\x*Mba Fhe Bak…®me enseri, mbe guigira mba ŇčiniŇčgi kambarav, mbe guigira ŇčkasŇčka bak…®me ki. Mbe ne nd…®knd…®gap, Guma Bak…®me n…®man buni mbat…®gir mba ŇčiniŇčgi ga nzuav, mbe nzuav, Guma Bak…®me nzuai fhuvara.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt Zu 1.10\x*Mba khesharigi gumgi, mbe ruaŇčruaŇčgi s…®gi fara muuŇčgiap, mbe nd…®knd…®gi ki fhuvara, mbe fhura sh…®sh…®ga rui. Mbe ruaŇčruaŇčgi s…®gi fara muuŇčgi guma, mbe fhura ana suirav, ana shogirim, ana rimgirga. Mbe kakagi bigi, mbe fhura buni mbat…®gir nta nzuai. Mbe mba s…®gi mbar…®gi t…®vara Fhe Bak…®me vh…®ra mba t…®vara mben muuŇčgirim, mbe mbat…®girga.
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt Ro 13.13; 1 Ko 11.20-21; Fi 3.19; Zu 1.12\x*Mbe zaagi gu simt…®gir harigi gumgi ga n…®…®Ňčgi, Fhe Bak…®me nen Ňčkar…®gar muuŇčgip, mben muunga. Mbe kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, raan mba k…®vgia pav, phara ŇčanŇčani k…®vgia pi ne, ne guigira ndikndigi t…®v ma. Mbe nde phorga pav, mbe nde mbuim, nde nzaŇčnzaŇčgim, mbe nden z…®rir farfagi. Mbe wo guiguigi t…®vi, mbe guigira ntan ndikndigi.
\v 14 Mbe zazera mbigi garav, r…®mgi phara tuav, ruarir mbe ndirgeŇč nd…®knd…®gi. Mbe mba t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui vuzvuk, mbe ana vh…®zgi fhuvara. Mbe guigira Zisas khoth…®gi nd…®knd…®k havhargi fhuv gumgi, mbe mben raaŇč shav, t…®vi mbat…®gir muun zav, mbe Ňčgi. Mbe vh…®ra harigi gumgi bigi garav nta niihi t…®vi, mbe guigira nta kaŇčgi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, Fhe Bak…®me guigira mben farfagirga.
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt Zu 1.11; VB 2.14\x*\x - \xo 2:15 \xt Nam 22.4-35\x*Mbe k…®r tuav guara segap, mbe fhura ŇčanŇčana mbui. Mbe Beor kama Baram vugi tuap, mbe anan vui. Ana t…®vi mbat…®gi ga muuŇčgiap, ana guigira mba t…®vi mbat…®gir vheza ndirgeŇč vuzvugi.
\v 16 Fhe Bak…®me Baram doŇčki ga muuŇčgim, ana guma fara muuŇčgiap kamthooŇč ntarav, Baram muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi ga nzuav, ana vhegi. Mba doŇčki maaŇč mba Fhe Bak…®me kamthooŇč guma ga muuŇčgim, ana mba ŇčanŇčangi nd…®knd…®ga mbat…®geŇč, ana ne thagi.
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 2:17 \xt Zu 1.12-13\x*Mba gumgi, mbe mbogi phara mbaagi fara muuŇčgi. Mbe vh…®ra buiva ph…®givige fara muuŇčgi. B…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč bak…®me zav nta sim, nta fhura tamtam vui. Fhe Bak…®me mbe nzuav muuŇčgi ŇčaneŇč guigira g…®ng…®ngiap, guigira ph…®…®gi, mbe mba Ňčanen k…®rga.
\v 18 \x - \xo 2:18 \xt FG 2.40; 2 Pi 1.4; 2.20; Zu 1.16\x*Mba gumgi, mbe fhura wari wo nzuai buni mbat…®gi ga nzuav ndikndigap, fhura tuava pura rui. Mbe fhura gumgi ndavi ga sav, ruarir mbigi ndir zav gumgi raaŇč shav, mbark…®rga t…®vi mbat…®gir wari wo fhavir muun zav mbe nzuai. Mbe mba t…®va mbuav, mba ntigera ndava vura t…®vi thagi gumgi, mbe mbe Ňčgim, mbe mba gumgi mbat…®gi z…®n vui.
\v 19 \x - \xo 2:19 \xt Zo 8.34; Ro 6.16; 1 Pi 2.16\x*Mba gumgi mbat…®gi khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNde nza z…®n Ňčg…®rga, nde b…®kb…®…®girga. Nde b…®kb…®…®gip, nde wari wo vuzvuga z…®n Ňčg…®p, nde za kha bigir muunga.‚ÄĚ Mbe maaŇč nzuav, mbe nduarira za mbat…®girga t…®vir Ňčaara gumgi ki. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, guma fhura t…®va thueŇč gan…®rim, ne ana gan…®nga, mba guma mba t…®ven Ňčaara guma ki.
\v 20 \x - \xo 2:20 \xt Mt 12.45; Ru 11.26; Hi 6.4; 2 Pi 1.2-4\x*Mbe guigira Zisas Krais kaŇčgi, ana nza Bak…®me ma. Ana vh…®ra taagia nza ndi guma ma. Mbe ne kaŇčgi nd…®knd…®k mben kurkurigim, mbe kha nuianan t…®vi mbat…®gi, mbe nta Ňčk…®…®i. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgip taagi Ňčg…®p, mba bigi phorg…®p ntan muunga, nta wom mbe keg…®rga, mbe guigira za mbat…®girga. Mbe fharav mba t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbuav, mbe mbat…®gi. Mba t…®vi mbat…®gi ntige wom mbe keg…®rim, mbe ntan b…®nan k…®rga, mbe guigi guarara za mbat…®girga.
\v 21 \x - \xo 2:21 \xt Ru 12.47-48; Zo 9.41\x*Mbe t…®vir vhuuiŇč tuav kaŇčgirga fhuv, ne nzerarga. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, mbe ntigem mba tuav kaŇčgiap, mbe Fhe Bak…®me nzuai t…®vi Ňčaari, mbe vh…®ra nta kaŇčgiap, nta ndigi. Mbe nta ndigap, wom k…®r nta segi.
\v 22 \x - \xo 2:22 \xt Snd 26.11\x*Mba mben hi t…®vi, nta guigira, mbe ntan vhunama sav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúFiaŇč ana viagiap, ana wom vov, wo viagi pi.‚ÄĚ Mbe nzuai kama mueŇč vh…®ra khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúDam ruagiap, wom vov, non…®ga ndogi.‚ÄĚ
\c 3
\s1 Guigi guarara Guma Bak…®me taagi zir…®rga.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt 2 Pi 1.13\x*Nde nan k…®vntogi guari, gu ntigem phenat…®t…®gap kha gava khergiap nde ndi mbai. Gu kha gavanin, gu nde nd…®knd…®gi khavi. Nde mba bigi ga nd…®knd…®g…®p, nden nd…®knd…®gi Ňčgaravra k…®rga.
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt Zu 1.17\x*Gu khueŇč vuzvugi, nde taagip mba zumgum h…®rga bigir buni ga nd…®knd…®g…®rga, mba buni Fhe Bak…®men kamthooŇč gumgi fhum nta bun suaŇčgi. Nde nta nd…®knd…®g…®p, nde vh…®ra Guma Bak…®me suaŇčgi t…®va nd…®knd…®g…®rga, ana taagia nza ndi Guma ma. Nde mba Zisas farasegi 12 th…®gi Ňčaara gumgi, Zisas han zav mba t…®va ndigap, ana bun nzuaim, nde mba t…®va mbararagi.
\p 
\v 3-4 \x - \xo 3:3-4 \xt 1 T 4.1; 2 T 3.1; 2 Pi 2.10; Zu 1.18\x*\x - \xo 3:3-4 \xt Ais 5.19; Jer 17.15; Ese 12.22; 12.27; Mt 24.48; Ru 12.45\x*Nde mba kaŇčgirga big…®na bak…®me khare, ne khaŇč muuŇčgi. Zisas taagi zir…®rga tuk han mbararga, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč nz…®…®i gumgi heg…®rga. Mbe heg…®p, wari won ndavi vuri vuzvugi mbat…®gi z…®n Ňčg…®rga. Mbe wari won ndavi vuri z…®n Ňčg…®p, Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč s…®…®Ňčv, khaŇč suanga, ‚ÄúAna khaŇč suaŇčgire, ana taagi zirga? Ana maaŇč suaŇčgiap, ana maaŇč ki? Ana zir…®rga fhuvara. Nzan nz…®gi fhum kav vh…®zgim, mba tugen kegap zav ntigem, kha bigi nta fhum Fhe Bak…®me kha nuian gu bigi ga muuŇčgim, nta mba ki mbugum mbara muuŇčgiap khar ki.‚ÄĚ
\v 5 \x - \xo 3:5 \xt Stt 1.6-9; Sng 33.6; Kor 1.17; Hi 11.3\x*Mbe tuituigip mba bigi ga nd…®knd…®g…®p, nta kaŇčgirgane thagi. Fhum guarara Fhe Bak…®me nzuaim, buip h…®gi. Fhe Bak…®me vh…®ra nzuav, mbaram mb…® kuvigim, nuian h…®gi.
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt Stt 7.11; 7.21; 2 Pi 2.5\x*Fhe Bak…®me zumgum nzuaim, mb…® h…®gap za kha nuiana phorgim, kha nuian mbat…®gi.
\v 7 \x - \xo 3:7 \xt Mt 25.41; 2 Te 1.8; 2 Pi 3.10\x*Ntigem, Fhe Bak…®me mba khesharigi kama mueŇčra suaŇčgi. Kha buip gum nuian, mani vhavar rarga khar ki. Vhav h…®g…®p, za mani shiv, manin farfagirga. Kha buip gum nuian, mani ntigem Fhe Bak…®me kha nuianan kav, k…®r Fhe Bak…®me segi gumgi gu mbigi muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi ga suaŇčv mbe suanga tugar rarga ki. Mba tugen, mba k…®r Fhe Bak…®me segi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe za mbat…®girga.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 3:8 \xt Sng 90.4\x*Nde nan k…®vntogi guari, nde kha bigeŇč nd…®knd…®k Ňčan…® thari. Guma Bak…®men nd…®knd…®gar, ana gari, ra bavira, ana 1,000 mpari fara muuŇčgi. Ana 1,000 mpari garim, nta ra bavira fara muuŇčgi.
\v 9 \x - \xo 3:9 \xt Ais 30.18; Hab 2.3; Ro 2.4; 1 T 2.4; Hi 10.37; 1 Pi 3.20\x*Gumgi mbari khaŇč nzuai, Guma Bak…®me wo suaŇčgi bigi, ana mbarara nta mbui. Gumgi mbari maaŇč nzuai. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Guma Bak…®me ana wo suaŇčgi bigi, ana mbarara nta mbui fhuvara. Ana guma the fh…®rgir…®g…®p Ňčgu mbat…®gar Ňčg…®rgane thagi. Ana khueŇč vuzvugi, kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi za ndavi dorg…®rga. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgiap, mbarara nde mbuav, nden rarga khar ki.
\s1 Kha nuian gu buip vh…®zgirga.
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 3:10 \xt Mt 24.29; 24.35; 24.43; Mk 13.31; Ru 12.39; 1 Te 5.2; Hi 1.11; VB 16.15; 20.11\x*Guma Bak…®me taagi zir…®rga tuk vhemkora h…®g…®rga, ana k…®…®i guma zi t…®var muuŇčgirga. Mba tugar buip furap, kh…®kh…®m bak…®me heg…®p, za vh…®zgirga. Fhe Bak…®me kha nuian gu buiva muuŇčgi bigi, nta za vhav nta shigirim, nta za vh…®zgirga. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, kha nuian gum mbe ana muuŇčgi bigi, nta khar ki, nta wom keg…®rga fhu. \f a \fr 3:10 \ft Kha vezar mbe Grikar kaman suaŇčgi kameŇč ne tuituigiap h…®gi fhuvara. \f*
\v 11 MaaŇč muuŇčgip, nde nd…®knd…®g…®, kha bigi mba t…®vara muuŇčgip vh…®zgirga. Nde ram muuŇčgi nd…®knd…®ga mbui? Nde ram muuŇčgi t…®va z…®n Ňčg…®rie? Nde wari won ruru t…®vi gu bigi ndiv, Fhe Bak…®me farve kh…®ngip, nde ana n…®man t…®vir Ňčaarira z…®n Ňčg…®p, nde Fhe Bak…®men t…®vi, nde zam nta z…®n Ňčg…®ri.
\v 12 \x - \xo 3:12 \xt Ais 34.4; Mai 1.4; 1 Ko 1.7; Ta 2.13; 2 Pi 3.10\x*Nde mba t…®va z…®n Ňčg…®p, nde Fhe Bak…®me tuga h…®rgen rarg…®p, wari k…®ri. Nde k…®v, mba tugar vh…®g…®p, wari k…®ri, mba tuk vhemkora h…®g…®rga. Mba tugar kha buip shiv za vh…®zgirga. Mba vhava shir…® guigira k…®vgip shiv, Fhe Bak…®me kha buiva muuŇčgi bigi za shiv, za mb…® geg…®rga. \f b \fr 3:12 \ft 2 Pita 3.9 khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúGuma Bak…®me zi fhuv ne khaŇč muuŇčgi.‚ÄĚ Ana tugar za kha gumgir n…®…®Ňčgirim, mbe za ndavi dorg…®rga. MaaŇč muuŇčgip, kha gumgi gu mbigi, mbe za wari won ndavir Fhe Bak…®men n…®…®nga. Mba t…®v, ana Guma Bak…®me taagi zir…®rga tuga ndi han z…®rga. Ndu FG 3.19 keg…®p, gan…® Ňčg…®p, ves 21 th…®g…®ri. \f*
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Ais 65.17; 66.22; VB 21.1; 21.27\x*Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčgi, ana nuiana kaman muuŇčv buiva kaman muuŇčgirga, mba nuianan k…®rga gumgi gu mbigi za t…®vir vhuuiŇčra muunga. Nza mba bigeŇč h…®r za mbuim, nza nera rargap, khar ki.
\s1 Nza tuituigira wari gan…®v, Guma Bak…®men rarg…®p, wari k…®rga.
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt 1 Ko 15.58; Fi 1.10; 1 Te 3.13\x*Nde nan k…®vntogi guari, nde mba bigi h…®r za mbuim, nde ntan rarga wari ki. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde khaŇč t…®g…®p havhargip, wari won ruru t…®vi gu bigi gan…®v, nde Fhe Bak…®me n…®man Ňčgaravra k…®v, nde big…®n thueŇč suaŇčv simt…®k k…®rga fhu. Nde Fhe Bak…®me phorg…®v ndava bavira k…®ri. Guma Bak…®me taagi zir…®rga tugar, Fhe Bak…®me nde gan…®nga, nde ndavi mb…®rarga.
\v 15 \x - \xo 3:15 \xt Ro 2.4; 1 Pi 3.20; 2 Pi 3.9\x*Nza Guma Bak…®me nzan rargap, ana mbarara nza mbuav ki. Nde khueŇč kaŇčgiri, ana maaŇč mbui, ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, ana taagia nza ndir za mbui. Fhe Bak…®me nd…®knd…®ga vhuuŇč guarara nzan fek Por ga n…®…®Ňčgi. Ana vh…®ra mba kameŇč khergiap, nde ndi mbarigi.
\v 16 \x - \xo 3:16 \xt Ro 10.3; 1 Ko 15.51; 1 Te 4.15\x*Ana kheri gavi, nta zam kha kameŇč nzuai. KhueŇč guigira, kha gavir ki buni mbari, nta nt…®…®riveŇč za k…®rar h…®gi fhuvara. Nza nta nt…®…®riveŇč kaŇčgi zav, nta nzuav Ňčaara mbat…®ga mbui. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, bigi kaŇčgi fhuv gumgi gum mba Zisas Krais khoth…®gi nd…®knd…®k havhargi fhuv gumgi, mbe pham kha buni bun nzuav, vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gavar ki buni, mbe vh…®ra pham nta nzuai. Mbe maaŇč mbui, mbe nduarira warira farfagi, mbe za mbat…®girga.
\v 17 \x - \xo 3:17 \xt Mk 13.5; 13.23; 13.33; 1 Ko 10.12; Ef 4.14; 2 Pi 1.10-12\x*Nde nan k…®vntogi guari, nde mba zumgum h…®rga bigi, nde nta kaŇčgi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde tuituigira wari gan…®ri. Nde fhura Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčgi t…®vi daasui gumgi gan…®rim, mbe nde guigira Zisas khoth…®gap, th…®ga havhargi nd…®knd…®gi Ňčg…® thari.
\v 18 \x - \xo 3:18 \xt Ef 4.15; 2 T 4.18; 1 Pi 2.2; Zu 1.25; VB 1.6\x*Nza Bak…®me Zisas Krais, ana taagia nza ndi guma ma. Ana nden kora mbuim, nde tuituigiap ana kaŇčgi. Nde fhura Kraisan kora muumbara gan…®rim, ana nde ndavi havhar…®rim, nde guigira ana kaŇčgiri. Ana guigira z…® bak…®me ki. Nza ana z…® ndiv vun kuamkuav, nza vh…®ra zazera mbara muuŇčgip ana z…® ndiv vun kuamkuarga. Ne guigi guarara.
